A mixin library for SASS that lets us write styles really effing fast.
Watch for updates: http://sass-lang.com/docs/yardoc/file.SASS_CHANGELOG.html

Example

---------------- styles.sass ----------------
@import "ss/shorthand.sass"

.logo
  background: #FF0000
  +s(100,100,400,200,a)
  
  &:hover
    background: #FF00FF
  
screenshot of styles.sass: http://cl.ly/3F3q3h3j0W041F2G3L0f